    • Field Detail

      • PREDICATE_PARAMETER_NAME

        public static final java.lang.String PREDICATE_PARAMETER_NAME
        This constant defines the name of the query parameter that can be set on the finder query to specify a query predicate.

        Note: Working with this query parameter is only meant to be done in the framework code! No application code should rely on this constant nor on the behavior related to the predicate parameter.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
